So these are all indications everywhere

14:56.160 --> 14:58.200
in the biological literature of the niche tenant

14:58.200 --> 15:02.760
relation as applied to bodies and things like bacteria.

15:02.760 --> 15:05.480
And you find it also in the literature on gynecology

15:05.480 --> 15:06.600
all over the place.

15:06.600 --> 15:08.360
Else the line just didn't see it.

