15:19.800 --> 15:26.200
It's a painful operation, but it's not a substantial change.

15:26.200 --> 15:27.240
So what makes a part?

15:27.240 --> 15:29.920
First of all, we're interested in parts

15:29.920 --> 15:34.400
on the inside of the organism, like the tub of yogurt

15:34.400 --> 15:34.880
in the roof.

15:34.880 --> 15:37.080
Being connected is not good enough.

15:37.080 --> 15:40.320
