20:15.920 --> 20:17.840
that the function of one entity

20:17.840 --> 20:20.040
is to perform the function of another entity.

20:20.040 --> 20:22.200
The whole point of having a function

20:22.200 --> 20:23.800
is that you have to perform it.

20:23.800 --> 20:26.240
All of these things are things which have functions.

20:26.280 --> 20:28.280
Of their own.

20:28.280 --> 20:30.640
So what she said is a bit like saying,

20:30.640 --> 20:33.000
the function of this biscuit is to enable

20:33.000 --> 20:36.720
the performance of the cooking function of my stove

20:36.720 --> 20:38.160
or of my chef.

20:38.160 --> 20:41.520
Or the function of this gash is to enable the performance

20:41.520 --> 20:43.720
of the slashing function of my scimitar.

20:44.680 --> 20:46.720
Or the function of this engine air filter

20:46.720 --> 20:48.760
is to enable the performance

20:48.760 --> 20:51.840
of the engineering function of the automobile engineer.

20:51.840 --> 20:53.960
It just doesn't make sense.

20:53.960 --> 20:55.680
But there is a fourth criterion

20:55.680 --> 20:57.920
because we saw processes have functions

20:57.920 --> 20:59.600
which contribute to the realization

20:59.600 --> 21:01.920
of the goals of the host,

21:01.920 --> 21:03.880
but they are not parts of the host.

21:03.880 --> 21:06.480
In order to be a part in the biological sense,

21:06.480 --> 21:09.480
the entity in question has to be generated

21:09.480 --> 21:13.880
by the coordinated expression of the organism's own genes.

21:13.880 --> 21:18.560
And that's a standard thesis from standard anatomy.

21:18.560 --> 21:20.040
That's how they work out

21:20.040 --> 21:22.960
what the anatomical parts of the organism are.

21:22.960 --> 21:26.880
I'll give you cloned embryos elsewhere.

21:26.880 --> 21:30.040
But all other embryos are on this criterion,

21:30.040 --> 21:31.880
not parts of the mother

21:31.880 --> 21:33.920
because they are not expressions

21:33.920 --> 21:36.720
of the mother's own genes.

21:36.720 --> 21:38.640
All right, so the reason why no one ever argued

21:38.640 --> 21:40.200
